{"title":"井冈龙泉夜夜鸣","authors":["敏歧"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":3,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈龙泉夜夜鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敏歧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜宿茨坪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四山响泉声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听泉声呵梦不成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声撩动我多少情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"索性披衣推枕起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山涌涌月正明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听泉声呵我问泉声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是不是在怀念老红军？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你身旁搭野营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百里清溪炊烟升；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你身旁磨战刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗飘出青竹林；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你身旁饮战马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过云峦去长征；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈一别四十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你夜夜怀念到天明？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望山月呵听泉声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思潮飞过岭千层——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大渡河上涛声急呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫草地压雨云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六盘山上风怒号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣园红日孕黎明……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看哪一片云朵下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有脚印叠脚印？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今这山青明月夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈泉呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在谆谆告诉后代年青人？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜这泉声呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有更深的情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞泉万道从天来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直下青峰如电奔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈龙泉——裁天剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十年磨洗到如今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当他切齿愤魍魉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜夜在山谷作龙吟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听今夜呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锵锵锵，嘭嘭嘭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵好似鼓角声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"召唤井冈儿女守哨口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着先辈足迹去出征！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜泉声响到明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泉声激励战士心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为斩鬼魅荡妖氛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈龙泉夜夜鸣！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}